            <p class="page-summary"><strong>Renovation storage in Vernal Utah</strong>. Temporary mouse-proof storage for furniture and belongings during home remodeling. From <strong>$130/month</strong>. Same-day move-in. Fort Knox Self Storage at <strong>2225 South 3250 East, Vernal, UT 84078</strong>. Call <a href="tel:4358287710">435-828-7710</a>.</p>
